Shortcuts (~/.i3/config, ~/.i3/shortcuts)
-----------------------------------------

<f1>         => help (this window)
<alt><esc>   => launcher (requires dmenu)

<altgr><k>   => close app (kill -15)
<altgr><l>   => close app by name (requires dmenu)
<altgr><m>   => mail (requires mutt,gnupg)
<altgr><M>   => magnifier (requires magnifier)
<altgr><i>   => instant messaging (requires irssi,gnupg)
<altgr><n>   => network app (requires wicd)
<altgr><f>   => file browser (requires pcmanfm)
<altgr><p>   => play/stop music (requires mpd)
<altgr><P>   => music player (requires mpd,ncmpcpp)
<altgr><¿>   => play next track (requires mpd)
<altgr><´>   => play previous track (requires mpd)
<altgr><.>   => increase volume
<altgr><->   => decrease volume
<altgr><x>   => X11 multimonitor menu (requires dmenu,xrandr)
<altgr><s>   => search song in mpd (requires dmenu,mpd)
<altgr><t>   => tell something (requires dmenu,mplayer)
<altgr><c>   => countdown (requires dmenu)
<altgr><v>   => launch virtual machine (requires dmenu,vbox)

<ctrl><+>    => increase font size (require terminal,firefox)
<ctrl><->    => decrease font size (require terminal,firefox)
<ctrl><C>    => copy to clipboard
<ctrl><V>    => paste from clipboard

<win><enter> => open terminal (requires urxvt)
<win><space> => open buffer terminal (fast)

<win><n>     => change focus to <n> desk
<win><N>     => move app to <n> desk
<win><->>    => change focus to next desk
<win><<->    => change focus to previous desk
<win><h>     => change focus to left window
<win><l>     => change focus to right window
<win><j>     => change focus to upper window
<win><k>     => change focus to down window
<win><H>     => move app to the left
<win><L>     => move app to the right
<win><J>     => move app up
<win><K>     => move app down

<win><m>     => mark an app
<win><'>     => go to a marked app

<alt><rshift>       => change keyboard layout

<ctrl><alt><supr>   => session menu (requires dmenu)
<ctrl><alt><l>      => lock screen (requires i3lock)

<ImpPt>             => screenshot (requires scrot)
<alt><ImpPt>        => selective screenshot
<win><ImpPt>        => start screencast (requires ffcast)
<win><alt><ImpPt>   => start selective screencast
<win><shift><ImpPt> => stop screencast
<Control><ImpPt>        => start gif selective screencast (requires ffcast,convert)

Modes
-----

<win><f>     => change to fullscreen mode
<win><d>     => change to default mode
<win><s>     => change to vertical stack mode
<win><a>     => change to tabbed mode

<altgr><z>   => enter resize mode
    <h>      => +1 px to the left
    <l>      => -1 px to the right
    <j>      => -1 px down
    <k>      => +1 px up
<altgr><x>   => exit resize mode

<win><insert> => inserts app into buffer mode (advanced)

<win><shift><space> => window toggle mode
<win><righ click>   => move
